---
title: White Fish & Parmesan Potato Salad with Celery Slaw
description: Eat the rainbow with this tasty mix of flavours. Fresh white fish gets a lightly spiced coating, with a warm, creamy potato salad and a crunchy celery slaw to round out the meal.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
